WEBVTT

00:02.040 --> 00:05.040
- There's no turning you, is there?
- No.

00:05.080 --> 00:06.760
Then I'll take you as you are.

00:06.800 --> 00:08.680
You, my friend, don't know who I am.

00:08.720 --> 00:11.840
Never come back to
Herot. You're dead to me.

00:11.880 --> 00:13.760
Play the part your
mother has set for you.

00:13.800 --> 00:16.239
She'll not be expecting when
we take power from her.

00:16.280 --> 00:18.040
Do you want to be Thane?

00:19.880 --> 00:22.800
Tell my uncle I am done with him.

00:22.840 --> 00:25.040
You have hid in the
shadows for too long.

00:25.080 --> 00:26.880
If you want power, take it.

00:26.920 --> 00:29.840
If I tell my mother the
truth, I'll lose her trust.

00:29.880 --> 00:32.439
And with it, any chance of ever ruling.

00:32.479 --> 00:34.720
But if Abrecan
attacks, Herot could fall.

00:34.760 --> 00:39.240
I have a vision for
us... to be the greatest tribe.

00:41.320 --> 00:44.400
Abrecan is going to attack Herot.

00:46.000 --> 00:52.074
